==Useful Info==
'''Jessica the Apprentice Sorceress''' is a weak [[unique]] caster found very early on. She's generally pretty harmless and extremely fragile, but she occasionally generates with an attack [[wand]] that can make her dangerous.

==Location==
*[[The Dungeon]]:2-3

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Melee combatants should lure her around a corner and destroy her at close range. Ranged fighters should simply blast her on sight; she has such low life that she'll fold quickly no matter what. The only time she's a serious threat is if she manages to slow a melee fighter at range and can kite you for several turns, or if you're a caster out of MP with no means of escape.

[[Category:Human]]
